      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks but it doesn't really help. it's not just \"struggles.\" it's like the person who made everything make sense is just... gone. and now everything feels pointless. i look at the bed and i see his side and it's just so heavy. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. everything is just grey.",
